```

---

## PowerShell Practice

List services

```powershell
Get-Service
```

Running services

```powershell
Get-Service |
Where Status -eq Running
```

Stopped services

```powershell
Get-Service |
Where Status -eq Stopped
```

Print Spooler

```powershell
Get-Service spooler
```

Restart service

```powershell
Restart-Service spooler
```

Automatic services not running

```powershell
Get-CimInstance Win32_Service |
Where {
    $_.StartMode -eq "Auto" -and
    $_.State -ne "Running"
}
```

